author: Angie (Sweet Sidekick)
title: Walgreens Photo: Personalized Collage Fleece Blanket Only $15 Shipped (Regularly $59.99)
text:
Through 2/18, Walgreens Photo is offering up 75% off + FREE shipping on this 40×60 Collage Fleece Blanket when you use the code BLANKETDEAL at checkout. This blanket is priced at $59.99 which means after the code BLANKETDEAL you’ll pay just $15 shipped.
This Personalized Collage Fleece Blanket is made of a soft poly-fiber jersey fleece and can feature up to 30 photos! This would make for an awesome Valentine’s, Mother’s Day or Father’s Day gift!
